  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this study is to determine the vulnerability of mood-related neurocircuitry in
      Parkinson Disease (PD) using deep brain stimulation of the subthalamic nucleus (STN DBS).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
